---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Get the Book & Leave a Review — The Mind's Gambit">
  <nav>
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a href="/" class="nav-logo"><img src="/images/logo.jpg" alt="Mind's Gambit" style="height:55px;width:55px;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;border:2px solid #c8a84e;margin-left:10px;vertical-align:middle;" /></a>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog" class="active">Reviews</a></li>
        <li><a href="/#documentary" class="nav-btn">Documentary</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="reviews-page">
    <section class="reviews-hero">
      <div class="pawn">&#9823;</div>
      <h1>The Mind&rsquo;s Gambit</h1>
      <p class="reviews-subtitle">The book is complete.</p>
      <p class="reviews-intro">The chapters that once lived here now live where they belong &mdash; in the book. <em>The Mind&rsquo;s Gambit</em> is available now in ebook, paperback, hardcover, and audiobook.</p>
      <div class="reviews-cta">
        <a class="btn-primary" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0H85FT7RD" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#128214; Get the Book on Amazon</a>
        <a class="btn-secondary" href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/255157692-the-mind-s-gambit" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Rate it on Goodreads</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="thankyou-card">
      <span class="thankyou-badge">A thank-you for early readers</span>
      <h2>First 10 print readers &mdash; a $10 gift on me</h2>
      <p>The first <strong>10 readers</strong> to buy the <strong>paperback or hardcover</strong> and email their name to <a href="mailto:bouajaja.m@gmail.com">bouajaja.m@gmail.com</a> will receive a <strong>$10 Amazon gift card</strong> as a simple thank-you. And if <em>The Mind&rsquo;s Gambit</em> stayed with you, an honest review on Amazon or Goodreads is always appreciated.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="reviews-ask">
      <h2>Your review would mean a great deal</h2>
      <p>If the book spoke to you &mdash; if a chapter stayed with you, or an argument changed how you see the game &mdash; please consider leaving a short review on <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0H85FT7RD" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Amazon</a> or <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/255157692-the-mind-s-gambit" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Goodreads</a>. A few honest sentences from a reader is the single best way to help a new book find the people who need it. Thank you for reading.</p>
      <p class="signoff">&mdash; Mourad Bouajaja</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.reviews-page, .reviews-page * { opacity: 1 !important; }
.reviews-page { min-height: 100vh; padding-top: 80px; }
.reviews-hero { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
.reviews-hero .pawn { font-size: 3rem; color: #f5efe2; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.reviews-hero h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 3rem; color: #c9a84c; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.reviews-subtitle { font-size: 1.3rem; color: #f0ece4; opacity: 0.85 !important; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-style: italic; }
.reviews-intro { font-size: 1.05rem; color: #b8b2a6; line-height: 1.7; max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
.reviews-intro em { color: #f0ece4; }
.reviews-cta { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.btn-primary { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg,#c9a84c,#d4b556); color: #0f111c; padding: 0.85rem 1.7rem; border-radius: 10px; font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.9rem; text-decoration: none; box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(201,168,76,0.35); }
.btn-secondary { display: inline-block; background: transparent; color: #e8e0d0; padding: 0.85rem 1.7rem; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.5); font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.9rem; text-decoration: none; }
.thankyou-card { max-width: 640px; margin: 1.5rem auto 0; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; background: rgba(201,168,76,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.35); border-radius: 14px; }
.thankyou-badge { display: inline-block; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: #c9a84c; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.thankyou-card h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.4rem; color: #f0ece4; margin: 0 0 0.85rem; }
.thankyou-card p { font-size: 1rem; color: #b8b2a6; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0; }
.thankyou-card a { color: #c9a84c; text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
.thankyou-card strong { color: #f0ece4; }
.reviews-ask { max-width: 640px; margin: 2.5rem auto 5rem; padding: 2.5rem 2rem 0; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15); }
.reviews-ask h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.5rem; color: #c9a84c; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.reviews-ask p { font-size: 1rem; color: #b8b2a6; line-height: 1.8; }
.reviews-ask a { color: #c9a84c; text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
.reviews-ask .signoff { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-style: italic; color: #f0ece4; }

nav { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 1000; background: rgba(15,17,28,0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.1); }
.nav-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 1rem 2rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
.nav-logo { font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: #c9a84c; text-decoration: none; }
.nav-links { list-style: none; display: flex; gap: 2rem; align-items: center; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
.nav-links a { color: #f0ece4; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; transition: color 0.3s; }
.nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active { color: #c9a84c; }
.nav-btn { border: 1px solid #c9a84c; padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem; border-radius: 4px; }
@media (max-width: 768px) { .reviews-hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; } .reviews-cta { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; } }
</style>
